name: TP_001_DECENTRALIZED_BLUE
description:
DECENTRALIZED is kinetic poster design by Maxime Archambault  (Canada/Quebec). It is in the collection Typo poster and it is the number one. In this collection the artist explores letters, movement and digital philosophy.
- GREY version as an edition of 10 
- BLUE version as an edition of 3 ***
- GREEN version as an edition of 1
